## Quick Reference — Output Files

| Step | Agent | Output | Key data it provides |
|------|-------|--------|---------------------|
| 1 | Creative Strategist | `strategy.md` | Angle, palette, category, format |
| 2 | Storyboard Architect | `storyboard.md` | Scenes, recipes, choreography, palette |
| 3 | Art Director | `art-direction.md` + SVGs | Proportioning, asset strategy, animation groups |
| 4 | Prompt Director | `{Name}Ad.tsx` | Working Remotion composition |
